WEBVTT

00:06:59.122 --> 00:07:00.479
When it comes to exercise,

00:07:00.503 --> 00:07:04.250
store all the equipment that you need
for a certain activity together,

00:07:04.274 --> 00:07:05.971
charged and ready,

00:07:05.995 --> 00:07:08.153
so you don't spend energy looking for it.

00:07:08.558 --> 00:07:11.875
And decrease temptations,

00:07:11.899 --> 00:07:14.312
for anyone driven by sugar cravings.

00:07:14.336 --> 00:07:15.526
Anyone?

00:07:15.550 --> 00:07:17.101
Say aye, go ahead.

00:07:17.125 --> 00:07:19.320
That itself is its own form of Crazy Mode

00:07:19.344 --> 00:07:22.172
and self-medication for Crazy Mode,

00:07:22.196 --> 00:07:24.545
but stop working your willpower.

00:07:25.077 --> 00:07:27.085
Design differently.

00:07:27.800 --> 00:07:29.934
If a food is out of immediate reach,

00:07:29.958 --> 00:07:32.948
such that you have to use
a stool to reach it,